Moogle Pass

Moogle Pass
610 Gems
+ Increased Point Bonus (30 days)
+ Guaranteed red passive abilities
from high eidoja (30 days)
+ Skip-Quest Ticket × 10

In addition to gems that come with the purchase of a Moogle Pass, you will also receive the following effects and items:
• Increased point bonus for 30 days from purchase
 • Guaranteed red passives from high eidoja
 • Skip-quest tickets
The count will be calculated by the in-game date, with one day passing at 08:00 UTC.

*The effect begins the moment of purchase, and lasts for 30 days from the following 08:00 UTC.

E.g.:
If you purchase the pass on October 30 at 02:00 UTC, the count starts from October 30 at 08:00 UTC, and it will remain effective until November 29 at 07:59 UTC.

Increased Point Bonus

During Effect period
Enhancement points, summon points, wild points, illusion points, spiritus points, and single-challenge points will receive a bonus of 150% (points × 2.5).
The enhancement point limit for each event will also be increased by 200%.
(You can obtain 15,000 points during a single event.)

*The increased point limit will still apply for a Moogle Pass purchased after an event begins.
If your Moogle Pass expires while an event is ongoing, the increased point limit will remain in effect for the duration of the event.

Guaranteed Red Passives from High Eidoja

While a Moogle Pass is active, passive abilities acquired from high eidoja are guaranteed to be acquired as red passives.


Skip-Quest Tickets

Skip-quest tickets are also included with the purchase of a Moogle Pass.





Moogle Pass Upgrade

You can upgrade an active Moogle Pass to a Premium Moogle Pass on the Purchase Moogle Pass screen by tapping Upgrade and purchasing the Moogle Pass Upgrade.


Upgrade Summary

Moogle Pass Upgrade
4,040 Gems
+ Additional Premium Mission Rewards
+ Moogle Token × 2
+ EX Power Token × 5
+ Additional Increased Point Bonus (Enhancement Points Only)
＋Skip-Quest Ticket × 20

*The price of an upgrade is slightly higher than the price of a standalone Premium Moogle Pass. Exact prices may vary by region.

*A currently active Moogle Pass will become ineligible for upgrade when renewed before its original expiration. To upgrade a currently active Moogle Pass, please purchase the Moogle Pass Upgrade before purchasing a renewal.

Refer to the game guide below for more details on additional premium rewards.

Premium Moogle Pass

Moogle Pass Renewal

You can renew your Moogle Pass or Premium Moogle Pass if there are two days remaining.
*Renewal is not automatic.

When you are able to renew, the remaining days will turn red on the Home and Increased Point Bonus screens.


When you renew, you can purchase either a Moogle Pass or Premium Moogle Pass.

You will be able to receive gems upon purchasing a Moogle Pass renewal, and the Moogle Pass 31-day bonus period will begin immediately after the currently active Moogle Pass or Moogle Pass Premium bonus period ends.

You will be able to receive gems and items upon purchasing a Moogle Pass Premium renewal, and the Moogle Pass Premium 31-day bonus period will begin immediately after the currently active Moogle Pass or Moogle Pass Premium bonus period ends.
